parameters: \n<Ameria>"Haa...! Haa...! I did it, I did it!"
\n<Ameria>"We did it, Lyric! The monster is somehow--"
\n<Lyric's voice>"Abababababa! Help me! Help me! I can't swim--!"

\n<Ameria>"Wait--!? It's okay, you can touch the bottom there! Calm
down!!"

\n<Lyric>"Cough! Cough! Ahh... I thought I was gonna die... for
real..."
\n<Lyric>"Okay my ass! Whose fault do you think this is!"
\n<Lyric>"Is following your sister's orders that important to you?"
\n<Lyric>"Then why? I'm a monster, you know."

Ameria performed a healing art on Lyric. The injury did not
heal.
\n<Ameria>"...You know, I want to become a splendid healer."
Ameria continued speaking in a whisper, looking down.

\n<Ameria>"...I once had a serious injury. But a priest healed that
wound for me. That's why I thought, I want to become a
healer like that priest."

\n<Ameria>"Lyric, you've lost your power and someone is targeting you,
right? I can't just leave you be. Because..."

\n<Ameria>"...Because I am a healer... I'm going to become a splendid
healer..."

Ameria performed a healing art on Lyric again. The injury
still did not heal.

\n<Ameria>"...But you know, I understand. I understand what you're
trying to say, Lyric."
Ameria slowly lifted her downcast face.
Her face was distorted with tears.

\n<Ameria>"It's a nuisance, isn't it? Being helped by someone like me,
you hate it, don't you?"

\n<Ameria>"I don't have any special talents. I don't have the power to
fight like my sister, nor do I have the talent for healing
arts like the priest."

\n<Ameria>"I'm no good in the dark. I'm scared of ghosts. I can't do
anything on my own. I've always been helped by my sister and
the priest."

\n<Ameria>"...That's why I thought I couldn't stay like this, and I've
been working hard all this time."

\n<Ameria>"I've read lots of books on healing arts, practiced a lot,
and worked really, really hard."

\n<Ameria>"...But it was no good. I couldn't become a splendid
healer."

\n<Ameria>"I've caused trouble for many people. I ran away. And then,
I was protected again. And I hurt someone important..."

\n<Ameria>"I couldn't bear the responsibility of being a healer... I
couldn't fulfill my duties..."

\n<Ameria>"It's an unwelcome favor, isn't it? You don't want to be
helped by someone like me, do you...?"

\n<Ameria>"I'm sorry. I'm so sorry... I'm sorry for being powerless...
I'm sorry for causing trouble..."
\n<Lyric>"I don't understand why you're apologizing to me."
As she said that, Lyric lifted Ameria's chin--
She kissed the lips wet with tears.
\n<Lyric>"A kiss. It cheers you up, right?"

\n<Lyric>"...I don't know what happened in your past. But even so,
there's no need for you to cry and apologize to me."
\n<Lyric>"And because you came to me, I am alive."
\n<Lyric>"How can I say that you're a bother to me with all that?"

\n<Lyric>"You don't need the power to fight or talent in healing
arts. They're not necessary for you."
\n<Lyric>"You can become one. A fine healer."
